{"word":"H92 - אֲגֻדָּה - ʼăguddâh - ag-ood-daw' - Bunch","slug":"H92","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֲגֻדָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼăguddâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ag-ood-daw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bunch"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05D2;&#x05D3;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - 'a&#x0306;gu&#x0302;dda&#x0302;h</b> - <i>ag-ood-daw'</i><p/>Feminine passive participle of an unused root (meaning to <i>bind</i>); a <i>band</i>, <i>bundle</i>, <i>knot</i>, or <i>arch: - </i>bunch, burden, troop."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H93\">H93</a>"}]}